.  </p>\r\n<p><b>Can I navigate through The AGSC using keyboard shortcuts?<br /></b>Sure thing! Were hoping you\'d ask. See the <a title="Keyboard Shortcuts" href="http://dev.theagsc.com//keyboard-shortcuts">Cheat Sheet page</a>.</p>', 'FAQ\'s', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 15:18:04', '2014-03-07 15:18:04', '', 15, 'http://theagsc.com/community/15-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ; 
