INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (296, 2, '2014-03-03 12:01:47', '2014-03-03 12:01:47', '<p><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Welcome to The Australian Graphic Supply Co.  We are so proud to release our business, and to announce that The AGSC is a partnership, owned and operated by us, Dave and Laura. </span></p>\n<p>We got married on the 3rd of December 2012. That day we forged an unbreakable team in marriage. On the 28th of February 2013 I left my full time job as a junior in a design agency in Sydney to start full time freelancing.  At the same time, Laura left her retail job, and together Laura and I created the AGSC - starting another unbreakable bond... in business. </p>\n<p>It turned out to be our best business decision to date; the harmony with which we work as family is the same harmony we bring to working together (thankfully). Here\'s a few words on why we work.<em> </em></p>\n<p><em>Laura – Managing Director</em><i><br /> </i>Laura has a wonderful brain for systems, organisation &amp; finances. If you email us you are likely to end up chatting to Laura (and be better off for it). She has a keen sense for good design - and <em>tells me</em> when I\'m not producing it. She\'s not one to tiptoe through any tulips; she was blessed with a frankness I can only dream of wielding. She is a fantastic photographer, and my favourite second shooter. Laura can juggle a remarkable number of processes at once, so is invaluable in keeping website development on track, updating our daily tasks, following up on projects and generally ensuring everything is running smoothly for our clients.</p>\n<p>She\'s also an extremely handsome woman, but that doesn\'t tend to have as direct an impact on business. Still worth mentioning though.<em> </em></p>\n<p><em>Dave – Creative Director</em><br /> Dave is the most creative person I know.  My earliest memories of Dave from when we had first met were of him drawing cartoons on customers’ invoices; he was always seemingly creating, no matter the time or place.  Dave’s passion for the design world is the driving force behind The AGSC.  He is an incredibly hard working designer, who strives for the best.  He doesn’t take no as an answer, and is always thinking outside of the box, trying to create bigger and better.  Dave has a great eye, whether that be for lettering, website design, photography, music; he is simply incredibly gifted.  Dave exudes lettering – it has become a huge of our lives, and an integral part of our business. </p>\n<p>I love that Dave exudes such an energetic, exuberant personality; continually finding reasons to laugh, and make this already incredible job more rewarding.</p>\n<p>We are incredibly proud and excited to be finally releasing The AGSC, and making our partnership in business known to the world.  We cannot wait to share more with you about ourselves, about our business, and about design. </p>\n<p>Dave and Laura</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'The \'us\' in The Australian Graphic Supply Co', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '286-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-03 12:01:47', '2014-03-03 12:01:47', '', 286, 'http://newsite.theagsc.com/community/286-autosave-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ; 
