INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (595, 2, '2014-03-05 21:31:06', '2014-03-05 21:31:06', '<p><b></b><em>Travel Series</em></p>\n<p>We have lived in <a href="http://daveandlaura.in/spain/photography/friends-meet-oviedo" target="_blank">Oviedo</a> for a little over 4 months now, and we have fallen in love with the quaint, small, beautiful city that is nestled in-between snowy mountains, and beautiful coast.  Oviedo is a place that will always be dear to us, and whilst we’ve been here, we’ve been developing a font named after it.  This is a sneak peak of what it will look like.</p>', 'Oviedo', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '411-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-05 21:31:06', '2014-03-05 21:31:06', '', 411, 'http://theagsc.com/community/411-autosave-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ; 
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (352, 1, '2014-03-04 14:05:47', '2014-03-04 14:05:47', '<p><b>Client:</b> MV3 Global PTY LTD</p>\r\n<p>We were really excited to start working on the branding of an event called ‘Horizon’ being held in June 2014 in Sydney.  It’s an event held to bring passionate and driven people together to take charge of their lives and to become the author of their own destiny.  The client wanted to focus on ‘direction\', and from this, an aeronautical theme began to emerge.  The strong, bold Horizon is edited from the font Futura, with the compass linking the name to the overall theme of the event.  Further branding like brochures, day books and ticket sleeves are to be completed in the coming month.</p>', 'Horizon', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '261-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-04 14:05:47', '2014-03-04 14:05:47', '', 261, 'http://newsite.theagsc.com/community/261-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ; 
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (358, 2, '2014-03-04 15:12:58', '2014-03-04 15:12:58', '<p><b>Client:</b> Carlos Alvarez<br /> <b>URL:</b> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">http://alvarez.is/</span></p>\r\n<p>Carlos is a talented theme developer, who designs beautiful templates using bootstrap and WordPress.  He was one of our first Spain-based clients that we worked with before moving there.  He is one of the friendliest clients we have worked with, and it was so much fun to get to know him a little, and work together on his logo.  He wanted a minimal and simple logo that didn’t compete with his theme designs on his website.  This was a really fun project to work on, as the relationship between the letters in ‘Alvarez’ gave us a lot to work with.  </p>', 'Alvarez', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '255-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-04 15:12:58', '2014-03-04 15:12:58', '', 255, 'http://newsite.theagsc.com/community/255-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ; 
