INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (398, 2, '2014-03-04 19:10:32', '2014-03-04 19:10:32', '<p>Client: <em>Jamie Oliver</em></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Art Direction: <em>Adrienne Pitt</em></span><b></b></p>\r\n<p>When the art director for Jamie Oliver contacted us about doing a lettering piece for the front cover of their upcoming issue, we could not have been more stoked.  We have always loved Jamie Oliver’s cooking, his style, and his attitude in the kitchen, so it was a great honour to be able to participate creatively with him in some way.  The magazine issue was all about latin flavours, which we found very appropriate as we were preparing our move to Spain.  </p>', 'Jamie Oliver Magazine', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jamie-oliver-magazine', '', '', '2014-03-05 21:36:00', '2014-03-05 21:36:00', '', 0, 'http://newsite.theagsc.com/?post_type=work&#038;p=398', 12, 'work', '', 0) ; 
