d understood your project we can give you a quote.  Send us an email (LINK) or head over to our contact form to get in touch with us!<br /> <br /> <b>Do you accept rush jobs?<br /></b>We understand that some projects have a tight deadline, and we would love to help you out with that!  For an additional fee, we accept rush jobs; shoot us an email with the details of the project, and the deadline, and we’ll see what we can do!<br /> <br /> <b>What’s the best way to reach you?<br /></b>The best way to reach us is through our email (hello@theagsc.com), or through our contact form.  Our office hours are 8:30am - 5:00pm (CET), so if we receive emails outside of this time we will get back to you as soon as possible, within business hours. <br /> <br /> <b>Do you code websites?<br /></b>One of the biggest joys in designing websites, is that step where you take a design, and make it live.  There is such beauty in turning something static into a functional site, and we pride ourselves on our coding ability.  We also sometimes contract out to an amazing developer for those trickier processes (web apps etc…), and he is one of the best in the business.<br /> <br /> <b>What is your lettering process?<br /></b>Take a look at our lettering process blog here.<br /> <br /> <b>How long do projects normally take?<br /></b>Our hand lettering jobs (logos, lettering commissions etc…) normally take between 3 - 6 weeks to complete, with websites taking between 2 - 3 months.  However, this is just rough ball park, as every project will differ depending on the scope of the job.  <br /> <br /> <b>Can I navigate through The AGSC using keyboard shortcuts?<br /></b>Sure thing! </p>', 'FAQ\'s', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-05 01:40:38', '2014-03-05 01:40:38', '', 15, 'http://newsite.theagsc.com/community/15-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ; 
