INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (671, 1, '2014-03-06 01:06:14', '2014-03-06 01:06:14', '<p>Hello! Welcome to The Australian Graphic Supply Co, an Australian design studio and creative community run by Dave and Laura Coleman. While you’re here, we recommend you take a look at <a title="Work" href="http://dev.theagsc.com//work" target="_blank">our work</a>, visit the <a title="Shop" href="http://dev.theagsc.com//shop" target="_blank">shop</a>, score a free texture or two, check out a tutorial, buy a print, or even learn some keyboard shortcuts to make getting around our new digs easier.</p>\r\n<p>So who are we? We are Dave and Laura, we’re super in love, got married in December 2012, and decided to quit our jobs early 2013 to start what is now The AGSC. We are enormously passionate about design - oof, especially lettering - and working together on creative projects for clients whose businesses and ventures we believe in. Here\'s a little video so you can put faces to the names.</p>\r\n\r\nhttp://youtu.be/AgVk3RdK2js\r\n\r\n<p>Laura – <em>Managing Director<br /></em>Laura has a wonderful brain for systems, organisation &amp; finances. If you email us you are likely to end up chatting to Laura. She has a wicked eye for design, and is a gifted photographer. Her relationship with photoshop is getting pretty serious, too. She’s the one that keeps this operation on track. She is the most supportive, patient, encouraging and talented person I know. </p>\r\n<p>Dave -<em> Creative Director<br /></em>Dave’s passion for the design world is the driving force behind The AGSC. He is the most creative person I know. He’s an incredibly hard working designer, who constantly strives for the best. Dave exudes lettering – it has become a huge part of our lives, and an integral part of our business. His energetic, exuberant personality and his ability to continually find reasons to laugh makes this already incredible job even more rewarding.</p>\r\n<p>We are so proud and excited to be finally releasing The AGSC, and making our partnership in business known to the world.  We cannot wait to share more with you about ourselves, about our business, and about design.</p>\r\n<p><em>Dave and Laura</em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'The \'us\' in The Australian Graphic Supply Co', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '286-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-06 01:06:14', '2014-03-06 01:06:14', '', 286, 'http://theagsc.com/community/286-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ; 
